1
00:00:58,080 --> 00:00:58,880
I know the rules

2
00:00:59,800 --> 00:01:01,040
But you're so damn hot, Sis

3
00:01:02,240 --> 00:01:03,960
It's hard not to whip out my gun

4
00:01:04,640 --> 00:01:06,240
On the General's turf

5
00:01:07,040 --> 00:01:08,080
What gun?

6
00:01:09,360 --> 00:01:10,840
You'd better behave

7
00:01:13,120 --> 00:01:14,160
Thanks for the reminder, Sis

8
00:01:14,440 --> 00:01:16,120
So you'll let us in now, right?

9
00:01:18,880 --> 00:01:19,520
Give it to me

10
00:01:28,840 --> 00:01:29,520
Let's go

11
00:01:31,120 --> 00:01:32,080
Thanks, bro

12
00:01:37,040 --> 00:01:38,640
Shen Xingyu losing it just now...

13
00:01:38,840 --> 00:01:40,120
She's probably not working for Sis Fei

14
00:01:40,520 --> 00:01:41,920
She's Zhao Wudi's

15
00:01:59,720 --> 00:02:01,120
The General is here!

16
00:02:20,600 --> 00:02:21,440
And this is...?

17
00:02:21,640 --> 00:02:22,680
My name's A Di

18
00:02:22,680 --> 00:02:23,480
Did I ask you?

19
00:02:25,480 --> 00:02:25,960
General

20
00:02:26,840 --> 00:02:29,280
Sis Fei heard it's your birthday today

21
00:02:29,640 --> 00:02:31,960
So she had me bring you a birthday gift

22
00:02:32,240 --> 00:02:33,560
May you have boundless blessings

23
00:02:33,960 --> 00:02:35,080
And a long life

24
00:02:36,320 --> 00:02:37,120
My birthday?

25
00:02:37,560 --> 00:02:39,040
She thinks this is kids playing house

26
00:02:39,800 --> 00:02:41,360
Bringing a gift this pathetic

27
00:02:43,600 --> 00:02:44,480
There's a bomb in here!

28
00:02:55,600 --> 00:02:56,360
Nobody move!

29
00:03:01,800 --> 00:03:02,360
General!

30
00:03:02,360 --> 00:03:03,920
We spotted Sis Fei's men outside

31
00:03:04,240 --> 00:03:04,840
Got it

32
00:03:05,720 --> 00:03:06,560
Keep scouting

33
00:03:06,720 --> 00:03:07,080
Yes, sir!

34
00:03:08,720 --> 00:03:09,680
You've got some nerve

35
00:03:10,160 --> 00:03:10,960
Pretty wild

36
00:03:11,760 --> 00:03:12,560
I like it

37
00:03:13,120 --> 00:03:14,560
Why point a gun at me?

38
00:03:15,080 --> 00:03:16,320
Wanna go down together?

39
00:03:16,720 --> 00:03:18,680
It's all Sis Fei's people outside now

40
00:03:19,240 --> 00:03:19,960
If we go out,

41
00:03:20,240 --> 00:03:21,680
we'll get turned into Swiss cheese

42
00:03:22,200 --> 00:03:23,280
Either way, we're dead

43
00:03:24,040 --> 00:03:25,440
Might as well defuse the bomb first

44
00:03:25,840 --> 00:03:26,400
Defuse it

45
00:03:26,960 --> 00:03:27,680
Who's gonna do it?

46
00:03:28,480 --> 00:03:29,480
I sure as hell can't

47
00:03:30,360 --> 00:03:32,160
Wu Di has a special way of defusing bombs

48
00:03:32,840 --> 00:03:34,360
Why not try him?

49
00:03:36,000 --> 00:03:37,000
Why's everyone looking at me?

50
00:03:37,720 --> 00:03:38,480
I don't know how!

51
00:03:38,800 --> 00:03:39,840
I'm just the delivery guy

52
00:03:40,080 --> 00:03:41,120
Once I finish the job,

53
00:03:41,160 --> 00:03:42,080
I can leave

54
00:03:47,280 --> 00:03:47,960
Fine

55
00:03:48,760 --> 00:03:50,200
Since the pretty lady said so,

56
00:03:50,920 --> 00:03:51,680
you'll defuse it

57
00:03:53,680 --> 00:03:54,480
Defuse it

58
00:03:55,200 --> 00:03:56,440
Fine, I'll do it, okay?

59
00:04:15,120 --> 00:04:16,200
Can he do it?

60
00:04:21,720 --> 00:04:23,000
I must be crazy

61
00:04:23,000 --> 00:04:24,560
Seeing someone who looks like Wu Di

62
00:04:24,560 --> 00:04:25,960
and betting my life on him

63
00:04:41,880 --> 00:04:43,160
What a stupid method

64
00:04:44,000 --> 00:04:45,600
Could he really be Wu Di with amnesia?

65
00:04:52,880 --> 00:04:54,080
The cake Sis Fei picked is pretty good

66
00:04:54,520 --> 00:04:55,240
Real whipped cream

67
00:04:55,680 --> 00:04:56,320
You wanna try some?

68
00:04:57,040 --> 00:04:57,600
All right

69
00:04:59,640 --> 00:05:00,400
General Dawa

70
00:05:00,720 --> 00:05:01,720
Sorry for the offense

71
00:05:02,240 --> 00:05:03,080
You've got guts

72
00:05:05,960 --> 00:05:06,840
And skills

73
00:05:10,040 --> 00:05:10,840
All right

74
00:05:11,640 --> 00:05:12,560
Everyone,

75
00:05:12,840 --> 00:05:14,120
go hide in the basement for now

76
00:05:21,120 --> 00:05:22,360
We'll slip out when things get chaotic

77
00:05:22,920 --> 00:05:24,160
I'll take you somewhere in a bit

78
00:05:28,920 --> 00:05:30,640
Sis Fei tried to blow me up

79
00:05:32,400 --> 00:05:33,360
If she's playing ruthless,

80
00:05:33,880 --> 00:05:35,480
then don't blame me for fighting dirty

81
00:05:45,040 --> 00:05:45,760
Look around

82
00:05:52,120 --> 00:05:53,840
This is my secret base

83
00:05:57,680 --> 00:05:58,320
What are you doing?

84
00:06:00,320 --> 00:06:01,400
Taking that photo

85
00:06:01,800 --> 00:06:03,400
You're safe with me

86
00:06:08,840 --> 00:06:09,920
Maybe what you're seeing

87
00:06:10,280 --> 00:06:11,640
is the whole situation in Dongba

88
00:06:12,440 --> 00:06:13,960
Master Hong and Sis Fei

89
00:06:14,800 --> 00:06:16,240
each control their own turf

90
00:06:17,240 --> 00:06:18,120
Our restaurant

91
00:06:18,760 --> 00:06:20,080
sits right on the border

92
00:06:20,520 --> 00:06:22,680
It's a buffer zone

93
00:06:23,120 --> 00:06:24,160
And Master Hong and Sis Fei

94
00:06:24,280 --> 00:06:26,840
also show our boss, Sutai, some respect

95
00:06:28,960 --> 00:06:29,760
You're using me

96
00:06:30,680 --> 00:06:31,360
Using you?

97
00:06:32,360 --> 00:06:34,240
Sure, meeting Sis Fei and Dawa today

98
00:06:35,040 --> 00:06:36,120
was part of my plan

99
00:06:36,760 --> 00:06:37,960
But I didn't expect

100
00:06:38,440 --> 00:06:40,480
we'd end up at Dawa's military base

101
00:06:41,840 --> 00:06:43,120
We've never even met before

102
00:06:44,680 --> 00:06:45,360
So how am I using you?

103
00:06:46,560 --> 00:06:47,960
If you've never met me,

104
00:06:49,040 --> 00:06:49,840
why did you save me?

105
00:06:57,880 --> 00:06:59,120
This thing saved you

106
00:07:00,880 --> 00:07:01,760
But

107
00:07:02,040 --> 00:07:03,720
as for who exactly gave me the order,

108
00:07:04,720 --> 00:07:05,560
I don't know either

109
00:07:08,600 --> 00:07:09,400
Honestly, though,

110
00:07:09,880 --> 00:07:11,600
if I hadn't seen you with my own eyes,

111
00:07:12,440 --> 00:07:14,160
I'd have thought it was a prank

112
00:07:14,680 --> 00:07:17,080
(Get close to Dawa and draw out Master Hong)

113
00:07:19,960 --> 00:07:20,440
Oh, right

114
00:07:21,480 --> 00:07:22,360
Do you know Laiya?

115
00:07:23,240 --> 00:07:23,920
Ali

116
00:07:24,720 --> 00:07:25,960
She's a bounty hunter

117
00:07:26,320 --> 00:07:27,280
She's saved Wu Di a few times

118
00:07:27,280 --> 00:07:28,320
And tried to kill him a few times

119
00:07:28,520 --> 00:07:29,360
Friend and foe, I guess

120
00:07:31,680 --> 00:07:34,000
Looks like Dongba's about to get lively

121
00:07:49,160 --> 00:07:50,240
Your husband gave it to you?

122
00:07:52,200 --> 00:07:52,840
Yes

123
00:07:56,800 --> 00:07:58,240
I mean, as a woman,

124
00:07:58,960 --> 00:08:00,160
why come all by yourself

125
00:08:00,800 --> 00:08:02,000
to Dongba,

126
00:08:02,480 --> 00:08:03,640
and even go to Wuming Restaurant?

127
00:08:05,320 --> 00:08:07,120
A bitch named Youyou told me

128
00:08:07,440 --> 00:08:09,080
she knows who killed Wu Di

129
00:08:10,440 --> 00:08:11,560
So I had to come

130
00:08:13,560 --> 00:08:14,360
Youyou

131
00:08:35,760 --> 00:08:37,920
Zhao Wudi went missing in M City a year ago

132
00:08:38,080 --> 00:08:38,680
That's right, yeah?

133
00:08:39,680 --> 00:08:40,840
You've got news on the killer?

134
00:08:43,200 --> 00:08:44,640
This info...

135
00:08:45,240 --> 00:08:46,160
How much is it worth?

136
00:08:46,640 --> 00:08:49,200
Rumors aren't worth a dime

137
00:08:49,320 --> 00:08:51,640
This assassin's codename is Forty-Seven

138
00:08:52,080 --> 00:08:54,920
He belongs to a mid-tier hit group, Dark Night

139
00:08:55,080 --> 00:08:55,960
Ranked eighth

140
00:08:57,440 --> 00:08:58,880
A mid-tier hit group?

141
00:08:59,600 --> 00:09:00,600
Ranked eighth?

142
00:09:01,920 --> 00:09:03,560
How could he kill my husband?

143
00:09:04,200 --> 00:09:05,920
Even Jing Ke nearly killed the King of Qin

144
00:09:06,480 --> 00:09:07,280
Assassins, you know...

145
00:09:08,360 --> 00:09:09,920
Thirty percent skill

146
00:09:10,480 --> 00:09:11,480
Seventy percent luck

147
00:09:13,520 --> 00:09:15,800
After Forty-Seven finished the job,

148
00:09:15,800 --> 00:09:17,280
he never showed up again

149
00:09:18,320 --> 00:09:19,160
After that,

150
00:09:19,840 --> 00:09:22,440
word got out about Zhao Wudi's death

151
00:09:22,760 --> 00:09:23,920
If you get any other info,

152
00:09:24,200 --> 00:09:25,200
let me know immediately

153
00:09:25,760 --> 00:09:26,960
Money's not an issue

154
00:09:27,360 --> 00:09:28,440
Really?

155
00:09:29,000 --> 00:09:30,400
It's been a long time since I've met

156
00:09:30,400 --> 00:09:32,240
a boss this generous

157
00:09:33,040 --> 00:09:34,000
Sis

158
00:09:35,200 --> 00:09:36,440
Want me to...

159
00:09:36,560 --> 00:09:37,640
service you a little?

160
00:09:38,520 --> 00:09:40,040
No, thanks

161
00:09:42,280 --> 00:09:43,120
A Di

162
00:09:43,320 --> 00:09:44,600
Then come on

163
00:09:45,880 --> 00:09:47,600
I can't take it anymore

164
00:09:51,720 --> 00:09:52,680
Wait outside

165
00:09:53,240 --> 00:09:54,080
I'll go give her a poke

166
00:10:10,240 --> 00:10:11,080
That fast?

167
00:10:11,480 --> 00:10:12,360
It was just a shot

168
00:10:12,600 --> 00:10:13,440
Don't get any ideas

169
00:10:15,360 --> 00:10:16,200
Youyou

170
00:10:17,040 --> 00:10:18,000
She's a sex addict

171
00:10:18,360 --> 00:10:19,360
With a split personality

172
00:10:20,120 --> 00:10:22,080
They say it was from taking the wrong meds as a kid

173
00:10:22,600 --> 00:10:23,880
When she has an episode,

174
00:10:23,880 --> 00:10:25,320
she goes into town to find men

175
00:10:25,880 --> 00:10:27,280
If she can't find one she likes,

176
00:10:27,600 --> 00:10:28,880
she comes back to the safe house for me

177
00:10:29,240 --> 00:10:30,720
I use my special technique

178
00:10:30,720 --> 00:10:31,880
to help her vent her urges

179
00:10:32,040 --> 00:10:32,600
And of course,

180
00:10:33,280 --> 00:10:34,320
her other personality

181
00:10:34,440 --> 00:10:35,600
disappears with it

182
00:10:43,360 --> 00:10:44,680
Sis, you're charging with the ball

183
00:10:45,080 --> 00:10:45,960
That's a foul

184
00:10:47,160 --> 00:10:48,200
You little brat

185
00:10:48,880 --> 00:10:50,120
Sneaking off without a word

186
00:10:50,120 --> 00:10:51,520
is really damn rude

187
00:10:52,040 --> 00:10:53,560
The General requests your presence

188
00:10:54,280 --> 00:10:55,680
He wants to properly thank you both

189
00:10:57,600 --> 00:10:58,680
You're too kind, Sis

190
00:10:59,320 --> 00:11:00,520
The bomb's already been delivered

191
00:11:00,920 --> 00:11:02,080
House rules

192
00:11:02,080 --> 00:11:03,240
We keep debts and grudges clear

193
00:11:03,640 --> 00:11:04,840
We're even now

194
00:11:05,760 --> 00:11:07,600
You've got some strong hands, kid

195
00:11:08,000 --> 00:11:09,280
I just don't know

196
00:11:09,640 --> 00:11:11,040
if your stance is just as solid

197
00:11:11,640 --> 00:11:12,920
Or if you're hard down there

198
00:11:13,360 --> 00:11:14,520
That's on you, Sis

199
00:11:15,080 --> 00:11:16,000
You little brat

200
00:11:16,320 --> 00:11:17,440
If you wanna spar,

201
00:11:17,640 --> 00:11:18,760
I'll play with you when I've got time

202
00:11:19,000 --> 00:11:20,080
But this time,

203
00:11:20,080 --> 00:11:22,040
the General gave a strict order

204
00:11:22,280 --> 00:11:23,640
I have to take you two back

205
00:11:46,760 --> 00:11:49,160
See if that lady boss has strong backing

206
00:11:49,640 --> 00:11:50,800
To see if I can touch her

207
00:11:51,200 --> 00:11:52,000
Yes, sir

208
00:11:58,400 --> 00:12:00,360
They even gave us a room to sleep in

209
00:12:00,360 --> 00:12:01,520
I thought

210
00:12:01,520 --> 00:12:03,200
they'd throw us in a cell

211
00:12:03,720 --> 00:12:04,600
Looks like General Dawa

212
00:12:04,720 --> 00:12:06,280
isn't totally ungrateful after all

213
00:12:09,880 --> 00:12:11,280
So what now?

214
00:12:15,680 --> 00:12:16,480
Sleep

215
00:12:26,360 --> 00:12:28,280
Sleeping like a log

216
00:12:34,000 --> 00:12:34,800
All done

217
00:12:36,200 --> 00:12:37,200
Still hurt?

218
00:12:39,280 --> 00:12:40,680
How could it not hurt?

219
00:14:46,840 --> 00:14:48,760
This obedience drug really works

220
00:14:48,880 --> 00:14:49,960
A woman this wild

221
00:14:50,520 --> 00:14:52,440
gets as tame as a kitten

222
00:14:53,720 --> 00:14:55,680
This is the newest aphrodisiac

223
00:14:56,560 --> 00:14:58,760
Even the new club girls

224
00:14:58,880 --> 00:15:01,040
I only let them have one drop

225
00:15:13,240 --> 00:15:15,160
It's all gold bars and cash

226
00:15:19,240 --> 00:15:22,800
Dawa and Master Hong's private files

227
00:15:23,680 --> 00:15:25,480
Where would they hide them?

228
00:15:33,360 --> 00:15:34,600
(Shen Xingyu is in danger)

229
00:15:59,680 --> 00:16:01,320
Where are you going this late?

230
00:16:06,040 --> 00:16:07,920
I can't sleep at night

231
00:16:08,280 --> 00:16:09,560
so I wanted to go out

232
00:16:09,560 --> 00:16:11,840
to get some fresh air, that's all
